<Layout title='Music'>
  <TextWithPhoto title='Music' photo={twelve} alt='Robert singing on stage'>
    <blockquote>
      <p>
        “Practice any art, music, singing, dancing, acting, drawing, painting,
        sculpting, poetry, fiction, essays, reportage, no matter how well or
        badly, not to get money and fame, but to experience becoming, to find
        out what’s inside you, to make your soul grow.”
      </p>
      <cite>— Kurt Vonnegut</cite>
    </blockquote>
  </TextWithPhoto>
  <p class='text-center'>
    Music has been the thread that has stitched my life together. I cannot even
    imagine my life without music, without playing the guitar, writing songs, or
    singing with other people.
  </p>
