  <TextWithPhoto title='Camp Liberty' photo={seventeen} alt='Robert and Danny'>
    <p>
      Children <i>love</i> to sing! My 40 years of work with children taught me that
      young people should have the opportunity to sing every day, several times a
      day. Singing is an activity that brings joy and community into our lives.
    </p>
